data.title: 1950 Press Photo Birthplace of George Bernard Shaw in Dublin, Ireland
data.meta_description: This is an original press photo. His father was George Carr Shaw, retired civil servant who dabbled at being a corn broker. Photo is dated 07-28-1950. A: The short answer is no. It may contain wrinkles, cracks, and possibly even tears due to its age and how it was handled before it got to us.
